            "title": "港股下午初段微跌　滙控績後升逾1%　恒生急挫逾5%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股下午初段微跌，恒生指數較早時報22950點，跌25點，跌幅0.11%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">科技指數報5671點，升32點，升幅0.58%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滙控(00005)去年列帳稅前盈利及季度股息同樣好過預期，午後股價抽升逾1%，較早時報88.15元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">同系的恒生銀行(00011)業績公布後急挫逾5%，跌穿100元水平，較早時報99.3元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14717300-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e4%b8%8b%e5%8d%88%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e5%be%ae%e8%b7%8c%e3%80%80%e6%bb%99%e6%8e%a7%e7%b8%be%e5%be%8c%e5%8d%87%e9%80%be1%e3%80%80%e6%81%92%e7%94%9f%e6%80%a5%e6%8c%ab%e9%80%be5-2",
